_:N945efb444ecf4fbeb30688f0de4c20ed <http://schema.org/articleBody> "<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/office-for-investment-financial-services\">Office for Investment: Financial Services (<abbr title=\"Office for Investment: Financial Services\">OfI:FS</abbr>)</a> is a dedicated concierge service within the Office for Investment.</p>\n\n<p>By bringing together the different elements of the UK ecosystem, including the regulatory bodies, the <abbr title=\"Office for Investment: Financial Services\">OfI:FS</abbr> offers comprehensive and bespoke support in a structured, co-ordinated way to firms looking to establish and expand their presence in the UK.</p>\n\n<p>Our team of financial services experts operates in partnership with:  </p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/hm-treasury\"><abbr title=\"His Majesty's\">HM</abbr> Treasury</a> </li>\n  <li>\n<a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.fca.org.uk/firms/support-services\">Financial Conduct Authority</a> </li>\n  <li>\n<a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.bankofengland.co.uk/prudential-regulation/authorisations/new-firm-authorisation\">Prudential Regulation Authority</a> </li>\n  <li>\n<a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.theglobalcity.uk/OFI-Financial-Services\">City of London Corporation</a> </li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>We are focused on increasing the attractiveness of the UK’s financial services sector and supporting firms in navigating the regulatory landscape. This supports the <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/office-for-investment\">Office for Investment’s</a> wider objectives of securing investment that drives growth, job creation and increased productivity across the UK.</p>\n\n</div>" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
